{"tid":1478631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝你 輪椅叔叔 你令我相信香港人仍然係清醒","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T06:56:20.000Z","uid":160294,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8089205e70d3bc252e7272921dd7d43995058c","tid":1478631,"uid":160294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"頭先派818傳單個陣<br />\n派左俾一位行動不便坐住輪椅既叔叔<br />\n佢睇左一陣  特登返轉頭再同我講<br />\n佢寧願唔要政府派糖 唔要雙糧 唔要津貼 (希望冇記錯) 都想留返d錢醫好個女仔隻眼 <br />\n叔叔見我呆左 再重複多次<br />\n唔想雙糧 唔要津貼 都想醫好女仔隻眼<br />\n<br />\n雖然我個下想講女仔隻眼係永久失明 好唔返<br />\n但望到你既眼神 你既好意 <br />\n個下真係好感動 講唔出口<br />\n最後我眼濕濕望住佢離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叔叔叫我幫佢係連登開post<br />\n因為佢冇連登acc <br />\n就算而家開ac都係p牌 冇人會信<br />\n<br />\n叔叔我信守承諾 幫你開左post喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道你有睇連登架<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手推post推到佢見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你 呢個晚上我充滿力量繼續派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人 818見 <br />\n我愛香港"},{"pid":"2f3b848e1944ff1de4d96d318643899cec05764c","tid":1478631,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4874a93159a60b255ecf5ab9c18fb59f8f5f935c","tid":1478631,"uid":71129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8423658b17a32c84bb3648c6dc83b6d0a887c28","tid":1478631,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fe1a65f798fe8eb3275eec4e1cf6eb135a3036f","tid":1478631,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2